					<additions><p>F.1r: three seals including that of Polier (twice) and <persName xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" type="supplied" key="">Kamāl al-dīn Khān</persName>, dated 24 Shaʿbān in Shāhjahānābād. A note states that the work was written by <persName xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" type="supplied" key="">Abū Ṭālib al-Ḥusaynī</persName>. The same author's name appears in the text of f.1v, where it is also stated that the work covers the rule of Timur from age 7-74. It is a translation from a text in Turkic found in the library of a Yemeni ruler.</p> 
